                <div class="space-y-3 text-base" style="color: var(--color-text-secondary);">
                    <p class="font-semibold" style="color: var(--color-text-primary);">
                        When creating ANY new package or component, you MUST use the current theme system with CSS variables for all colors, backgrounds, borders, and text. <strong style="color: var(--color-primary);">All components are fully compatible with MAUI Blazor Hybrid.</strong>
                    </p>
                    <div class="p-4 rounded relative" style="background-color: var(--color-surface-2);">
